      "body" : "For what it&#39;s worth: I had this same problem even when using <code>LocalDate</code> and not <code>LocalDateTime</code>. The issue was that I had created my <code>DateTimeFormatter</code> using <code>.withResolverStyle(ResolverStyle.STRICT);</code>, so I had to use date pattern <code>uuuuMMdd</code> instead of <code>yyyyMMdd</code> (i.e. &quot;year&quot; instead of &quot;year-of-era&quot;)!"
