    "last_activity_date" : 1543936900,
    "creation_date" : 1543936900,
    "answer_id" : 53616125,
    "question_id" : 27454025,
    "content_license" : "CC BY-SA 4.0",
    "body" : "<p>This works fine</p>\n\n<pre><code>public class DateDemo {\n    public static void main(String[] args) {\n        DateTimeFormatter formatter = DateTimeFormatter.ofPattern(\"dd-MM-yyyy hh:mm\");\n        String date = \"16-08-2018 12:10\";\n        LocalDate localDate = LocalDate.parse(date, formatter);\n        System.out.println(\"VALUE=\"+localDate);\n\n        DateTimeFormatter formatter1 = DateTimeFormatter.ofPattern(\"dd-MM-yyyy HH:mm\");\n        LocalDateTime parse = LocalDateTime.parse(date, formatter1);\n        System.out.println(\"VALUE1=\"+parse);\n    }\n}\n</code></pre>\n\n<p>output:</p>\n\n<pre><code>VALUE=2018-08-16\nVALUE1=2018-08-16T12:10\n</code></pre>\n"
  }, {
    "owner" : {
      "account_id" : 1300889,
      "reputation" : 135,
      "user_id" : 1250830,
      "user_type" : "registered",
      "profile_image" : "https://www.gravatar.com/avatar/27b706d285aef8a1de2f50a3498257b6?s=256&d=identicon&r=PG",
      "display_name" : "beefsupreme",
      "link" : "https://stackoverflow.com/users/1250830/beefsupreme"
    },
    "is_accepted" : false,
    "score" : 0,
    "last_activity_date" : 1623184881,
    "creation_date" : 1623184881,
    "answer_id" : 67894311,
    "question_id" : 27454025,
    "content_license" : "CC BY-SA 4.0",
    "body" : "<p>I arrived at this problem because my input string didn't have a year in it:</p>\n<p>input string:  <code>Tuesday, June 8 at 10:00 PM</code><br />\nformatter:  <code>DateTimeFormatter.ofPattern(&quot;EEEE, MMMM d 'at' h:mm a&quot;, Locale.US);</code></p>\n<p>I knew the year so I just appended it to get:</p>\n<p>input string:  <code>Tuesday, June 8 at 6:30 PM 2021</code><br />\nformatter:  <code>DateTimeFormatter.ofPattern(&quot;EEEE, MMMM d 'at' h:mm a uuuu&quot;, Locale.US);</code></p>\n"
  }, {
    "comments" : [ {
      "owner" : {
        "account_id" : 17602579,
        "reputation" : 931,
        "user_id" : 12772224,
        "user_type" : "registered",
        "profile_image" : "https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/AAuE7mBh_fYCJcSHFzsTRzAhaPGTD8wYw3KSPcal86Nr=k-s256",
        "display_name" : "Mr. Doge",
        "link" : "https://stackoverflow.com/users/12772224/mr-doge"
      },
      "edited" : false,
